rem Computer
rem 8/28/2017

ifflag hosaka alarm
 [|
  do Bring Up Maintenance
   [
    print The latest maintenance records show that the system was last cycled five
    print days ago. Before that it's been over a month.
   ]

  do Test Cryotubes
   [
    print Alarms sound as the system starts to test the cryotubes. The scientists
    print monitoring the tubes back up, only to be blasted with liquid nitrogen
    print that sprays out of a ruptured valve. Panic ensues and the staff run.
    setflag test cryotubes
    setflag hosaka alarm
    go Cryogenics Lab
   ]

  do Cycle System
   [
    print Alarms start to sound as you cycle the system. The tubes shake,
    print scientists step back, and then a loud thud as liquid nitrogen is
    print flushed. The tubes crack open, and the scientists rush to help the 
    print creatures that fall out.
    setflag cycle system
    setflag hosaka alarm
    go Cryogenics Lab
   ]

   do Exit Computer
    [
     print You walk away from the terminal.
     go Cryogenics Lab
    ]
 ]
